Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.74,0:00:09.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的行人沒有想平常那樣推辭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.65,0:00:11.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有面紅耳赤地流鼻血呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.12,0:00:15.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  因為一直都受到鈴的幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.77,0:00:18.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾我也得做些讓小鈴感到高興的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.23,0:00:20.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.70,0:00:21.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.06,0:00:27.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼下面一起泡澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.94,0:00:34.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺這熱水一點都不熱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.27,0:00:37.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的  就算水一點都不熱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.89,0:00:41.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心裡卻感覺熱乎乎的非常溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.51,0:00:46.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.33,0:00:53.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.79,0:00:55.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.89,0:00:59.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是好澡堂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.32,0:01:01.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等 睡糊塗了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.35,0:01:03.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個不是浴室  是水缸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.14,0:01:05.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.17,0:01:09.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和行人一起的話  連心裡都熱乎乎的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.60,0:01:11.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說些聽不明白的夢話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.33,0:01:12.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點醒來  小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.57,0:01:14.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.13,0:01:23.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透明  透明
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.05,0:03:01.97,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感冒了…去取冰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.18,0:03:07.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.98,0:03:09.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧  小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.61,0:03:10.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.51,0:03:14.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡糊塗了在水缸中待了一夜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.37,0:03:15.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然會感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.34,0:03:16.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.13,0:03:18.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣呆看著她也沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.32,0:03:22.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能去取一些敷在頭上降溫用的冰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.51,0:03:23.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.50,0:03:26.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這沒有電  沒有冰箱的島上會有冰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.60,0:03:29.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能小看自然的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.27,0:03:31.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰這東西島上當然是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.24,0:03:43.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滑溜溜的  好像很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.97,0:03:48.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼最後一道工序在上面加上許多甜的蜂蜜的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.14,0:03:50.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼大家一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.88,0:03:52.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.32,0:03:56.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.38,0:03:58.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這種冰透的感覺真讓人無法抵抗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.69,0:04:11.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.40,0:04:13.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這邊沒有錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.54,0:04:17.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.24,0:04:19.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.18,0:04:21.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.88,0:04:24.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.79,0:04:26.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什麼 這麼突然的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.17,0:04:30.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可愛  果然你就是行人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.57,0:04:34.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來你和雪乃一模一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.46,0:04:35.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說是雪乃的姐姐?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.32,0:04:39.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.18,0:04:41.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  媽媽在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.67,0:04:42.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽…媽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.69,0:04:46.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是雪乃的媽媽 鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.87,0:04:48.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請叫我小鏡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.81,0:04:54.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼小鏡啊  擅自把熊熊和鴨鴨帶出來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.49,0:04:56.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家可都是有工作的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.57,0:04:57.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.73,0:04:59.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想稍微吃點冰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.50,0:05:01.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才讓熊熊它們陪我來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.96,0:05:04.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  明明上歲數了  還吃什麼刨冰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.35,0:05:08.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  誰上歲數了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.55,0:05:10.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰都會上歲數吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.11,0:05:14.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說回來  行人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.32,0:05:15.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時間的話不一起來玩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.25,0:05:19.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有點事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.30,0:05:21.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴感冒發燒了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.99,0:05:24.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴姐感冒了?  真少見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.82,0:05:26.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像那種平時越健康的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.61,0:05:28.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦發生什麼就越脆弱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.82,0:05:30.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俗話說柔能克剛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.40,0:05:32.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越堅硬越容易折斷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.88,0:05:34.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說些不吉利的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.93,0:05:38.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之是來為了取做冰敷用的冰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.39,0:05:42.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實從奶奶那裡聽說保管在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.29,0:05:43.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話  在那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.05,0:05:45.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來帶你去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.05,0:05:52.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來有這樣的洞窟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.34,0:05:55.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是島上最涼爽的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.94,0:05:58.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很適合保管冰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.03,0:06:03.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上草席  為使它不太容易融化
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.80,0:06:07.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.23,0:06:09.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.18,0:06:13.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才和熊熊們把它作成刨冰當點心吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.88,0:06:14.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.20,0:06:17.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部吃了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.57,0:06:18.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還剩下這些
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.82,0:06:22.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算收下已經添上蜂蜜的冰也沒用吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.38,0:06:25.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且只有這麼點的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.55,0:06:27.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿回去的時候就已經融化掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.94,0:06:28.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.88,0:06:30.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣就只能…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.64,0:06:35.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  等等  停下  停下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.93,0:06:37.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真頭痛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.00,0:06:39.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就沒有其他有冰的地方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.80,0:06:40.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.78,0:06:43.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能去山裡取了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.23,0:06:46.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山?  山是指哪裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.45,0:06:50.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富士山啊  在島上正中最大的山
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.06,0:06:52.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頂上不是積了許多雪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.15,0:06:55.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那裡把大量的雪取回來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.63,0:06:57.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再壓成冰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.96,0:06:58.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.50,0:07:01.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那快點去取吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.02,0:07:04.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想快點把冰拿給鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.44,0:07:05.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那倒是不錯的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.54,0:07:08.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過是非常辛苦  做好覺悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.23,0:07:09.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.12,0:07:11.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽就不用來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.26,0:07:15.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼  只留下我一個人  真狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.47,0:07:17.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽就算來也是累贅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.25,0:07:19.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.21,0:07:20.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是叫你帶我去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.97,0:07:22.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不老老實實把我帶去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.29,0:07:26.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你害羞的過去全部暴露給行人啊  可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.40,0:07:28.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請務必與我們同行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.97,0:07:32.78,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.49,0:07:34.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說  鏡與外表不同其實是非常容易暴躁的人?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.26,0:07:35.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.63,0:07:38.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說回來雪乃害羞的過去是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.60,0:07:40.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個有許多了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.46,0:07:57.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然仙貝不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.13,0:08:00.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這種熱天有刨冰就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.72,0:08:12.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說了別用這種方式叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.57,0:08:14.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能去稍微取些冰來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.73,0:08:21.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久沒有和大家一起出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.53,0:08:24.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  到了山頂大家一起打雪仗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.01,0:08:28.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要吧 我們不是特意去玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.09,0:08:30.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼去做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.09,0:08:34.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說是因為小鈴感冒發燒了去取冰…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.37,0:08:36.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候來的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.59,0:08:39.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴居然感冒了  真少見
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.00,0:08:41.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧  是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.36,0:08:44.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.55,0:08:45.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鞋帶斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.27,0:08:47.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且連黑貓都…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.94,0:08:49.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓開讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.50,0:08:50.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多麼的不吉利
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.13,0:08:53.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只不過是迷信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.78,0:08:55.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之得快點去取冰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.18,0:08:57.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見麻知  我得快點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.24,0:09:06.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  姐姐大人  真會使喚人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.19,0:09:07.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種小事自己去…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.87,0:09:11.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  下面是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.13,0:09:15.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あ「a」…い「i」…う「u」…え「e」…お「o」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.04,0:09:20.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這個難道是從麻知姐那得到的叫摩爾斯信號的東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.22,0:09:24.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.89,0:09:31.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰…的…話…行…人…大…人…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.22,0:09:37.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去…富…士…山…取…了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.39,0:09:43.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是完美的解讀了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.56,0:09:45.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在附近的話直接和我說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.98,0:09:57.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  行人稍微休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.99,0:09:59.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在那麼著急的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.71,0:10:00.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下要吃不消了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.17,0:10:01.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  對
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.10,0:10:04.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且到了山頂還要打雪仗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.86,0:10:07.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.36,0:10:12.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有還有  要做冰窟在裡面吃年糕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.29,0:10:15.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺能理解雪乃為什麼那麼努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.94,0:10:18.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽那麼孩子氣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.73,0:10:20.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.82,0:10:22.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加把勁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.15,0:10:42.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.97,0:10:45.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說了吧  很辛苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.53,0:10:49.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和外面的溫差很大  所以會感覺到格外寒冷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.78,0:10:52.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有寒冷症  特別怕冷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.12,0:10:55.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太陽落山後會更加冷的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.34,0:10:59.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我不會放棄的  小鈴在等著用冰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.78,0:11:02.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪乃和鏡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.71,0:11:04.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說在這大雪中走散了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.78,0:11:06.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡  行人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.36,0:11:10.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那種地方做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.82,0:11:13.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這裡最暖和了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.84,0:11:15.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.06,0:11:19.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山頂就在前面  先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.73,0:11:21.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.94,0:11:24.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎  雪乃也像這樣去不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.91,0:11:27.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼大的雪  要乘兩人飛翔是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.72,0:11:30.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  鷹鷹是媽媽優先的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.35,0:11:31.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.71,0:11:34.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鷹鷹是媽媽的青梅竹馬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.29,0:11:36.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以只要是媽媽的請求就不會拒絕的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.25,0:11:41.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  打中行人了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.27,0:11:42.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.44,0:11:44.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快  大家快點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.22,0:11:47.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就是山頂  快點開始打雪仗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.93,0:11:53.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這麼大的雪中  為什麼那人還那麼有精神
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.20,0:11:54.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.30,0:11:56.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘記我們的目的了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.99,0:11:58.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點把雪帶回去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.82,0:12:00.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.46,0:12:04.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然扔到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.64,0:12:06.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.81,0:12:08.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在才注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.33,0:12:12.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標是雪的話  沒必要要來山頂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.48,0:12:17.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但山頂還有好風景欣賞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.92,0:12:20.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過全是雪什麼都看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.96,0:12:25.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  行人要是早點說不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.73,0:12:26.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.98,0:12:27.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.76,0:12:32.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別反向我發脾氣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.55,0:12:34.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  不是我的錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.56,0:12:43.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過小鈴因感冒而臥床不起  也是機會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.17,0:12:46.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  在行人取冰回來之前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.55,0:12:48.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,襲擊熟睡的她  這回一定能贏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.91,0:12:54.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看那樣子  現在山頂附近是暴風雪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.15,0:12:57.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人應該不可能馬上回來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.61,0:12:58.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暴風雪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.42,0:13:01.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇難
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.38,0:13:07.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後  互相用體溫取暖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.36,0:13:10.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩人就這樣永遠的結合在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.14,0:13:13.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不是理小鈴的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.11,0:13:16.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紋次郎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.64,0:13:20.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著我  行人大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.83,0:13:30.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不覺得變大了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.57,0:13:32.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這麼點出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.58,0:13:34.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  不行  還不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.31,0:13:36.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取冰關鍵在回程的路上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.30,0:13:38.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算頂上是暴風雪  山下可是盛夏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.91,0:13:42.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去時得儘量讓雪不能融化
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.05,0:13:44.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經要回去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.89,0:13:47.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看  快看  年糕烤好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.35,0:13:49.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.81,0:13:51.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微休息一下走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.82,0:13:55.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在暴風雪停之前  就算出發也很困難的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.67,0:13:57.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  小鈴在等著
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.64,0:14:00.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要勉強才是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.48,0:14:02.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是從剛才開始就沒休息過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.18,0:14:05.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的  這不過這種程度
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.33,0:14:09.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讓人嫉妒  為了小鈴上刀山下火海
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.23,0:14:13.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了  不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.25,0:14:17.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  在這猛烈的暴風雪中勉強下山確實有點危險
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.77,0:14:21.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在冰窟中等風雪停比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.46,0:14:25.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  為了小鈴得儘快把冰送回去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.19,0:14:27.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道你很拼命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.69,0:14:30.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  行人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.18,0:14:36.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經和小鈴做過這種那種事情了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.92,0:14:43.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀  快看  快看  能讓鼻血瞬間凝固的寒冷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.49,0:14:45.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是亂來的話會凍死的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.04,0:14:46.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.96,0:14:48.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種東西第一次見到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.68,0:14:49.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.29,0:14:52.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別玩別人的鼻血
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.21,0:14:54.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之我還是要走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.03,0:14:58.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家就在冰窟裡等暴風雪停好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.46,0:15:09.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無論如何都要把這冰送給小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.59,0:15:11.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等  行人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.12,0:15:14.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪乃  很危險的  就留在這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.10,0:15:19.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.50,0:15:33.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.19,0:15:39.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來  哪裡是路完全不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.22,0:16:02.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.36,0:16:04.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊  小鈴更加痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.13,0:16:06.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能認輸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.77,0:16:12.70,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有急轉彎   小心跌落
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.60,0:16:31.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.81,0:16:55.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個好天氣  那麼溫暖  感覺想睡覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.42,0:16:59.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人  一起吃刨冰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.37,0:17:03.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比比看誰先吃完吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.02,0:17:06.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.30,0:17:07.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.71,0:17:09.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備  開始
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.84,0:17:27.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好危險  這樣睡過去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.73,0:17:29.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會被凍死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.13,0:17:35.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.54,0:17:45.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.01,0:17:48.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的  他是男孩子呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.85,0:17:53.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下  雪乃  雪乃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.20,0:17:59.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.08,0:18:04.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.01,0:18:13.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.09,0:18:18.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.96,0:18:24.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  還差一點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.59,0:18:32.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.89,0:18:35.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪乃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.55,0:18:36.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.65,0:19:09.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醬油
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.28,0:19:14.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給  醬油味的刨冰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.37,0:19:15.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能吃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.06,0:19:18.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好  不是做這種事情的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.88,0:19:27.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話  稍微能躲避一下日曬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.59,0:19:32.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.88,0:19:35.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微休息一下如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.88,0:19:39.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴在等著我  得儘快把冰送去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.58,0:19:42.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  真頑強啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.19,0:19:44.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鷹鷹  去幫幫他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.19,0:19:56.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  這樣下去在到之前就會全部融化了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.50,0:20:02.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好抓緊了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.08,0:20:22.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不害怕  不害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.39,0:20:32.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.33,0:20:39.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是去了哪裡閒逛到現在?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.28,0:20:41.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是去富士山去取冰了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.24,0:20:46.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  這個  已經那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.99,0:20:49.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.10,0:20:50.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.28,0:20:52.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感冒已經沒事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.70,0:20:54.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  完全好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.68,0:20:57.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來就不是大不了的感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.42,0:20:59.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡一天就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.48,0:21:03.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  那就好了  小鈴恢復健康了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.78,0:21:10.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.27,0:21:15.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是那麼喜歡亂來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.07,0:21:18.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在陽光這麼強烈的白天去富士山取冰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.99,0:21:20.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為溫差太大和過度疲勞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.89,0:21:22.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然會累倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.83,0:21:24.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  行人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.95,0:21:28.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  我又夢到行人了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.48,0:21:32.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和行人一起比賽看誰吃刨冰吃得快的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.56,0:21:33.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.28,0:21:36.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰沒浪費真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.31,0:21:40.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看這是行人拿回來的雪塊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.28,0:21:46.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.38,0:23:12.05,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&HE7A573}「好吃的 新娘修行」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.92,0:23:26.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.33,0:23:34.60,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}我來溫暖你…
